discussion_comments.comment_body:
this is not safe :(

``` javascript
var node = { style: { marginTop: 0, margin: 10 } };
```

``` javascript
// before
if ('marginTop' in node.style) {
  return node.style['marginTop'];
}
// returns 0
```

``` javascript
// after
return node.style['marginTop'] || node.style['margin'];
// returns 10
```
